{"title":"汉诺双塔","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"url":"http://www.tsinsen.com/A1162","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div id=\"pcont1\" style=\"margin-top:20px; display:block;\">\n"},{"title":"# 问题描述","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　给定A、B、C三根足够长的细柱，在A柱上放有2<i>n</i>个中间有孔的圆盘，共有<i>n</i>个不同的尺寸，每个尺寸都有两个相同的圆盘，注意这两个圆盘是不加区分的（下图为<i>n</i>=3的情形）。现要将这些圆盘移到C柱上，在移动过程中可放在B柱上暂存。要求：<br/>\n　　（1）每次只能移动一个圆盘；<br/>\n　　（2）A、B、C三根细柱上的圆盘都要保持上小下大的顺序；<br/>\n　　任务：设<i>A<sub>n</sub></i>为2<i>n</i>个圆盘完成上述任务所需的最少移动次数，对于输入的<i>n</i>，输出<i>A<sub>n</sub></i>。<br/>\n<img height=\"214\" width=\"358\" src=\"source/tsinsen/A1162/img/aHR0cDovL3d3dy50c2luc2VuLmNvbS9SZXF1aXJlRmlsZS5kbz9maWQ9cjg4QjJBZkU=.do\"/></div>"},{"title":"# 输入格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　一个正整数<i>n</i>，表示在A柱上放有2<i>n</i>个圆盘。</div>"},{"title":"# 输出格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　仅一行，包含一个正整数, 为完成上述任务所需的最少移动次数<i>A<sub>n</sub></i>。</div>"},{"title":"# 样例输入","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">1</div>"},{"title":"# 样例输出","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">2</div>"},{"title":"# 样例输入","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">2</div>"},{"title":"# 样例输出","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">6</div>"},{"title":"# 数据规模和约定","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　对于50%的数据，1&lt;=<i>n</i>&lt;=25<br/>\n　　对于100%的数据，1&lt;=<i>n</i>&lt;=200</div>"},{"title":"# 提示","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　设法建立<i>A<sub>n</sub></i>与<i>A<sub>n</sub></i><sub>-1</sub>的递推关系式。</div>\n\n</div>\n"}]}